headline: GTA Online
subtitle: The Multi-Floor Eclipse Blvd Garage
content:
It’s time to upsize and glamorize your vehicle collection. There’s a brand-new multi-floor garage property located right on Eclipse Boulevard in Los Santos with room for up to 50 vehicles, and unique amenities across five spacious floors.

This lavish new vehicular and social sanctuary is now available to purchase in GTA Online directly from Dynasty 8’s in-game website. GTA+ Members can claim theirs for free through March 15.
